The '''Nalroni Merchant Council''' was a group of appointed or elected [[Nalroni/Legends|Nalroni]] who monitored all trade conducted through the [[Celanon/Legends|Celanon]] starport in [[Celanon City]]. They were a very profitable organization due to the vast amount of trade conducted on Celanon.

[[Sykar]] was a representative for the Council.

